  <brief_title>Comparison of 6-fluoro-[18F]-L-dihydroxyphenylalanine (18F-DOPA) Positron Emission Tomography (PET) and Multiparametric Resonance Magnetic Imagery (RMI) in Initial Exploration of Glial Tumors</brief_title>
  <acronym>GLIROPA</acronym>
